    "description": "Hikari Business Form Co., Ltd. provides printing services in Japan. The company offers web solutions, including web and electronic form, SMS/email delivery, and website construction; data print processing services comprising full-color variable and address printing, cards, and barcode outputs; mailing services, such as enclosed and sealed, inspection equipment/check, matching, matching, and categorization, and post office delivery; business process outsourcing services consisting of application form receptions, survey results, my number reception, and year-end tax adjustments; and business form printing services for invoice, pressure-sealed postcards, seals and labels, environmentally friendly products. It also provides planning, production, commercial printing, and redesign services for brochures and flyers, universal designs, posters and stickers, and promotional material designs, as well as various tool creating services, including survey results reports, inventory management, and progress management. Hikari Business Form Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1968 and is headquartered in Hachioji, Japan."
